org.usfirst.frc.team2220.robot

Class Autonomous

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usfirst.frc.team2220.robot.Autonomous

  • public class Autonomous
extends java.lang.Object
    Autonomous utility functions.
    Piecing together these functions with different parameters allows for millions of different autonomous programs, if one is so inclined
    Currently utilizes the drivetrain, the collector and shooter
    Sensors used: Gyroscope, Camera
    Author:
    Josh

        public void turnGyro(double degrees,
                     double motorPower)
        Turns using the gyro First takes a reading, turns a number of degrees to a point, then nudges the robot back if it overshoots
        Parameters:
        degrees - Degrees to turn, positive to turn right, negative for left
        motorPower - Motor power for the inital turn, the second turn is motorPower - 0.1
